{"tid":1530843,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"請父母接送仔女返放學 以免受警隊欺凌","createTime":"2019-09-02T05:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T05:41:28.000Z","uid":265268,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aa01b02fdaa631e11989917b36d0da314c090b85","tid":1530843,"uid":265268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:21:19.000Z","msg":"各位中學生父母, 我知大家仔女已經長大, 接送返學係有啲肉酸.<br />\n但今日開學日, 大量防暴隊於各學校大門招呼 貴子女, 甚至有女同學於地鐵站被男警搜查.<br />\n事態嚴重, 貴子女<span style=\"color: red;\">人身安全受到極大威脅</span>.<br />\n警方聲稱唔好欺凌佢哋仔女, 但竟然帶頭欺凌各位仔女!<br />\n<br />\n懇請呼籲各位父母犧牲少少時間, 於非常時期, 陪同子女返學放學.<br />\n如果有人對 貴子女毛手毛腳, 請作出保護, 提醒 <span style=\"color: blue;\">我冇嘢講 我唔開鎖 警方無權搜袋</span> 等等原則, 保障 貴子女權益.<br />\n<br />\n父母對子女最大嘅關懷, 莫過於親身陪伴, 共渡艱難 🙏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pv6rDfi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPv6rDfi.jpg&h=427240ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dg6CKVj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDg6CKVj.jpg&h=ecac84e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dzcRPmY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdzcRPmY.jpg&h=612b7c03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cf9c5400baf0097e608641d6ac9df4f92b9ffbe","tid":1530843,"uid":265268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309c458042bb1e781ba4eb31f2533da7d0685752","tid":1530843,"uid":265268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e7526dbe7893c156bb811283dc15c3608d588